parameters.name: OrderActionDetail
parameters.description: The parameters that are used to filter SQL statements involved in the ticket.

parameters.name: OrderId
parameters.description: The ID of the SQL review ticket. You can call the [CreateSQLReviewOrder](~~257777~~) operation to query the ticket ID.

parameters.name: Tid
parameters.description: The tenant ID. You can call the [GetUserActiveTenant](~~198073~~) or [ListUserTenants](~~198074~~) operation to query the tenant ID.
